From 617d46454f7fc326a82e0901372d5d1ee665758d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Crescenzo <crescenzo@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 2 Jun 2026 01:50:48 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 2/4] dt-bindings: net: add Allwinner A733 GMAC0 compatible

Allow the A733 GMAC0 node to use the same Allwinner glue binding shape as
nearby mainline SoCs while retaining the existing A64 fallback.

The Cubie A7S vendor DTB places the active wired Ethernet MAC at
0x04500000, and mainline A523 already describes GMAC0 at the same address
with an SoC-specific compatible followed by allwinner,sun50i-a64-emac.
Using the same fallback keeps the first Ethernet slice on the existing
Allwinner DWMAC glue path, where syscon and RGMII delay handling already
live.

This only makes the compatible string schema-valid. It does not enable
Ethernet on the Cubie A7S board, choose PHY reset wiring, or claim that the
A733 delay values are tuned.

Signed-off-by: Crescenzo <crescenzo@gmail.com>
---
 .../devicetree/bindings/net/allwinner,sun8i-a83t-emac.yaml       | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/net/allwinner,sun8i-a83t-emac.yaml b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/net/allwinner,sun8i-a83t-emac.yaml
index 323a669fa982..2503936c01a0 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/net/allwinner,sun8i-a83t-emac.yaml
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/net/allwinner,sun8i-a83t-emac.yaml
@@ -40,6 +40,7 @@ properties:
               - allwinner,sun50i-h6-emac
               - allwinner,sun50i-h616-emac0
               - allwinner,sun55i-a523-gmac0
+              - allwinner,sun60i-a733-gmac0
           - const: allwinner,sun50i-a64-emac
       - items:
           - const: allwinner,sun55i-a523-gmac200
